When editing in Wiki Markup mode, placing a number of URLs with single line breaks in the following format:

{code:none}
http://example.invalid
http://anotherexample.invalid
http://thirdexample.invalid
{code}

Causes them to be rendered in Confluence as 

{code:none}
http://example.invalid http://anotherexample.invalid http://thirdexample.invalid
{code}

Adding an extra line break after each URL as in:
{code:none}
http://example.invalid

http://anotherexample.invalid

http://thirdexample.invalid
{code}

Causes URLs to be displayed with extra whitespace, like:
{code:none}
http://example.invalid

http://anotherexample.invalid

http://thirdexample.invalid
{code}

