The Confluence remote API provides methods to add groups and to add and remove space permissions for groups.  However, there are not methods to add global permissions for a group.

This means that there is no way to grant "can use" permissions to groups in bulk.

Many customers end up adding everyone to the confluence-users group as a workaround, but the customers I've heard from want the ability to "bless" existing groups in LDAP.

